<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      /* Using a dark aesthetic consistent with the blog's content [cite: 19] */
      body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #ffffff; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #0f0f0f; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
      
      /* Header uses a gradient similar to your index page  */
      .header { 
        padding: 40px; 
        text-align: center; 
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #8b5cf6, #4f46e5); /* Purple to Indigo  */
        border-bottom: 4px solid #4338ca;
      }
      
      .content { padding: 40px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; background-color: #050505; }
      
      /* Matching the CTA button to your index and about page indigo theme  */
      .cta-button { 
        background-color: #4f46e5; 
        color: #ffffff !important; 
        padding: 15px 30px; 
        text-decoration: none; 
        border-radius: 9999px; /* Pill shape  */
        font-weight: 600; 
        display: inline-block;
      }
      
      h1 { letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #ffffff; }
      .tag { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; }
      
      /* Feature box for newsletter updates [cite: 27] */
      .feature-box { background: #1e1e1e; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; border: 1px solid #374151; }
      .feature-title { color: #818cf8; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <span class="tag">ACCESS GRANTED</span>
        <h1 style="margin-top: 15px;">THE KUDO ARCHIVE</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2 style="color: #ffffff;">Welcome to the Archive, Karol.</h2>
        <p style="color: #d1d5db;">You have successfully joined <strong>The Kudo Archive</strong>—a space where passion for anime and manga meets thoughtful, in-depth reviews.</p>
        
        <div class="feature-box">
          <span class="feature-title">Inside the Archive</span>
          <ul style="color: #9ca3af; padding-left: 20px; margin: 0;">
            <li>Detailed, spoiler-free Anime & Manga Reviews.</li>
            <li>Real-time updates from my personal Anilist.</li>
            <li>Community discussions and deep-dives.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p style="color: #d1d5db; margin-bottom: 30px;">I watch whatever catches my eye—if a series manages to surprise me, it's guaranteed to get a review here.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="<%= @url %>" class="cta-button">BROWSE LATEST REVIEWS</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> The Kudo Archive.<br>
        You are receiving this because you subscribed to our newsletter[cite: 27].<br>
        <p style="font-style: italic; margin-top: 10px;">I hope you enjoy your stay!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>